-- Pier 1 February same-store sales fall 8.4 percent
-- 
-- Thu Mar 8, 2007 6:29am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/03/08/us-pier1-sales-idUSWEN520420070308

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Home furnishings retailer Pier 1 Imports Inc. ( PIR.N ) said on Thursday that its sales at stores open at least a year fell 8.4 percent in February. 


 Analysts on average had been expecting a same-store sales decline of 5 percent, according to a Reuters survey. Pier 1 said total sales for the five weeks ended on March 3 rose 14.3 percent to $120.5 million.